{"__ud_title":"12 条终端配置技巧，涵盖了从终端美化、权限管理到工作流自动化","__ud_tags":["Agentic Engineering","aiskills","vibecoding"],"__ud_update_time":1770982209962,"__ud_create_time":1770968012001,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"12-条终端配置技巧涵盖了从终端美化权限管理到工作流自动化"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"12 条终端配置技巧"},{"type":"text","text":"，涵盖了从"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"终端美化、权限管理"},{"type":"text","text":"到"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"工作流自动化"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"⚡️ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"12 条终端配置技巧"},{"type":"text","text":"，涵盖了从"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"终端美化、权限管理"},{"type":"text","text":"到"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"工作流自动化"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/dab0fde123624b28881b54470f6f56bd~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=X1UDIYuTYWT2B6m8fIuEpNtoXLM%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"回顾工程师们为何对 Claude Code 情有独钟，最突出的原因莫过于其"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"极高的可定制性"},{"type":"text","text":"：Hooks（钩子）、插件、LSP（语言服务协议）、MCP（模型上下文协议）、技能 (Skills)、Effort（思考力度）、自定义 Agent、状态栏以及输出风格等等。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"每位工程师使用工具的方式都不尽相同。我们在构建 Claude Code 之初，不仅致力于提供优秀的默认配置，更注重让它变得高度可配置。这也是开发者们爱上这款产品、以及 Claude Code 用户量持续加速增长的原因。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"以下是自定义 Claude 的一些常见方式："}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"1-配置终端环境-Configure-your-terminal"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. 配置终端环境 (Configure your terminal)"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"主题 (Theme)"},{"type":"text","text":" ：运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/config"},{"type":"text","text":" 切换明/暗模式。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"通知 (Notifs)"},{"type":"text","text":" ：启用 iTerm2 通知，或使用自定义的通知 Hook。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"换行 (Newlines)"},{"type":"text","text":" ：如果你在 IDE 终端、Apple Terminal、Warp 或 Alacritty 中使用 Claude Code，运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/terminal-setup"},{"type":"text","text":" 开启 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"Shift+Enter"},{"type":"text","text":" 换行功能（这样你就不用担心误触回车直接发送了）。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Vim 模式"},{"type":"text","text":"：运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/vim"},{"type":"text","text":" 开启。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/7aae527f23c347bbb840d95eb70536e3~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=xtGZJ9beCShHP7X2njyw4SjTMqc%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"2-调整思考力度-Adjust-effort-level"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 调整“思考”力度 (Adjust effort level)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/model"},{"type":"text","text":" 选择你偏好的 Effort Level（力度）："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Low"},{"type":"text","text":"：消耗更少 Token，响应更快。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Medium"},{"type":"text","text":"：行为表现平衡。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"High"},{"type":"text","text":"：消耗更多 Token，智能程度最高。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"text":"作者注：我个人习惯对所有任务都开启 High 模式。"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/bcb3b7e082504a5b9f205b6e59988f59~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=5xbBy2b4aRtGD%2B2%2B%2BBjeJBG5IwQ%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"3-安装插件MCP-和技能-Install-Plugins-MCPs-and-Skills"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. 安装插件、MCP 和技能 (Install Plugins, MCPs, and Skills)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"插件允许你安装 LSP（目前支持所有主流语言）、MCP、Skills、Agent 以及自定义 Hooks。你可以从 Anthropic 官方插件市场安装，也可以为你的公司创建私有市场。 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"建议："},{"type":"text","text":" 将 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"settings.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 提交到你的代码仓库中，以便团队成员自动添加这些市场配置。运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/plugin"},{"type":"text","text":" 开始使用。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ba797fb70cd54130961b49048be8be13~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=o7jQ8aMUi9%2FQw9V67LJ6VtYCrZ8%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"4-创建自定义-Agent-Create-custom-agents"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. 创建自定义 Agent (Create custom agents)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"要创建自定义 Agent，只需将 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".md"},{"type":"text","text":" 文件放入 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".claude/agents"},{"type":"text","text":" 目录。每个 Agent 都可以拥有自定义名称、颜色、工具集、预设允许/禁止的工具、权限模式以及指定模型。 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"冷知识："},{"type":"text","text":" Claude Code 有一个鲜为人知的功能，允许你设置主对话使用的“默认 Agent”。只需在 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"settings.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 中设置 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"agent"},{"type":"text","text":" 字段，或使用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"--agent"},{"type":"text","text":" 启动参数。 运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/agents"},{"type":"text","text":" 开始，或查看文档："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fsub-agents","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"sub-agents"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/f1d4beb58b6748a08df2cca39529f424~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=N%2FA9UiOjSYGrBm%2FqNrfEO0LWfos%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"5-预批准常用权限-Pre-approve-common-permissions"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. 预批准常用权限 (Pre-approve common permissions)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Code 采用了一套复杂的权限系统，结合了提示词注入检测、静态分析、沙盒机制和人工监督。开箱即用时，我们要预批准了一小部分安全命令。 如果你想预批准更多命令，运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/permissions"},{"type":"text","text":" 并将其添加到允许（allow）或阻止（block）列表中。记得将这些配置提交到团队的 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"settings.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 中。 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"支持通配符语法："},{"type":"text","text":" 尝试添加 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"Bash(bun run *)\""},{"type":"text","text":" 或 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"\"Edit(/docs/**)\""},{"type":"text","text":"。 了解更多："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fpermissions","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"permissions"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/168c01ff4a2d47b097de62516cd86ddb~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=bN79C1uZosW41r0icb%2BBMiud0FQ%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"6-启用沙盒机制-Enable-sandboxing"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"6. 启用沙盒机制 (Enable sandboxing)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"选择加入 Claude Code 的开源沙盒运行时（Sandbox Runtime），在提高安全性的同时减少权限确认弹窗。 运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/sandbox"},{"type":"text","text":" 启用。沙盒在你的本地机器上运行，支持文件隔离和网络隔离（Windows 支持即将推出）。 了解更多："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fsandboxing","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"sandboxing"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ecf63ae5c2524b4c8a0e258486929886~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=hDevqOqjDnSxYQCERzMXt3wncK8%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"7-自定义状态栏-Add-a-status-line"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"7. 自定义状态栏 (Add a status line)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"自定义状态栏会显示在输入框下方，你可以让它显示当前模型、目录、剩余上下文窗口、Token 成本，以及任何你在工作时想看到的信息。 Claude Code 团队里的每个人的状态栏都长得不一样。使用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/statusline"},{"type":"text","text":" 开始配置，或者让 Claude 根据你的 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".bashrc"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":".zshrc"},{"type":"text","text":" 自动为你生成一个状态栏。 了解更多："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fstatusline","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"statusline"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/e37e1afe474c49ba98c0db8a686e846c~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=cKkHEoq%2BsEw0%2BAHbIbYFzHeOGPI%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"8-自定义快捷键-Customize-your-keybindings"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"8. 自定义快捷键 (Customize your keybindings)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你知道 Claude Code 的每一个按键绑定都是可定制的吗？ 运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/keybindings"},{"type":"text","text":" 重新映射任何按键。设置支持热重载（Live reload），修改后立即生效，方便你调试手感。 了解更多："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fkeybindings","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"keybindings"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/5967ab53ac444b1997eae28a5fa7e275~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=Rzu2LFJLd%2F9oAgIMwkn3egPwR1s%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"9-设置钩子-Set-up-hooks"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"9. 设置钩子 (Set up hooks)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hooks（钩子）是一种以确定性方式介入 Claude 生命周期的机制。你可以用它来："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"将权限请求自动路由到 Slack 或 Opus 进行审批。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当 Claude 结束一轮对话时，通过 Nudge（轻推）让它继续工作（甚至可以触发另一个 Agent 或用提示词判断是否需要继续）。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"对工具调用（Tool calls）进行预处理或后处理，例如添加自定义日志。 让 Claude 帮你添加一个 Hook 试试看。 了解更多："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Fhooks","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"hooks"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/82cd07872de54d6d92bd3a3d973af2e4~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=1MDpCYERlPdGDQmKzL2BAoh%2FPeI%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"10-自定义加载文案-Customize-your-spinner-verbs"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"10. 自定义加载文案 (Customize your spinner verbs)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"正是这些小细节让工具变得更有“人味儿”。让 Claude 自定义它的 Spinner Verbs（加载状态动词），添加或替换默认的加载提示语。将 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"settings.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 提交到版本控制，与团队分享这些有趣的文案。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ac3dbb4da35a4ef3a1652af1b81b8921~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=5IP8VcDRDM6sWYDy2SvVRrqjIdw%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"11-使用输出风格-Use-output-styles"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"11. 使用输出风格 (Use output styles)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"运行 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/config"},{"type":"text","text":" 并设置 Output Style，让 Claude 以不同的语气或格式回应。"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"推荐："},{"type":"text","text":" 在熟悉新代码库时，启用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"explanatory\"（解释型）"},{"type":"text","text":" 风格，让 Claude 一边工作一边解释框架和代码模式。"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"推荐："},{"type":"text","text":" 使用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"learning\"（教学型）"},{"type":"text","text":" 风格，让 Claude 指导你进行代码更改。 你也可以创建自定义输出风格，调整出你喜欢的 Claude “嗓音”。 了解更多："},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://link.juejin.cn?target=https%3A%2F%2Fcode.claude.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Foutput-styles","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":null}}],"text":"output-styles"}]},{"type":"image","attrs":{"src":"https://p3-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/b3323ea19f384df49eafb5f425febe31~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAgVmliZV9CbG9vbQ==:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1771493497&x-signature=efNTYAN6uSt7NlAX4h1SKo0DSe8%3D","alt":"image.png","title":null}}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":4,"id":"12-万物皆可定制Customize-all-the-things"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"12. 万物皆可定制！(Customize all the things!)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude Code 开箱即用，体验极佳。但在你进行自定义配置后，请务必将 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"settings.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 提交到 Git，这样你的团队也能受益。 我们支持多种配置层级：针对特定代码库、针对子文件夹、针对个人，或通过企业级策略统一配置。 只要是你想要的行为，基本都能配置。我们支持 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"37 项设置"},{"type":"text","text":"和 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"84 个环境变量"},{"type":"text","text":"（建议在 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"settings.json"},{"type":"text","text":" 中使用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"env"},{"type":"text","text":" 字段，避免编写复杂的包装脚本）。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}